WEBVTT

00:01.000 --> 00:03.093
male announcer:
LAST SEASON ON PSYCH...

00:03.130 --> 00:05.360
- MR. YANG IS THE MOST
NOTORIOUS KILLER

00:05.400 --> 00:06.537
THIS CITY HAS NEVER SEEN.

00:06.570 --> 00:08.037
HE ONLY RESURFACES
WHEN HE FEELS

00:08.070 --> 00:09.037
THERE'S A WORTHY OPPONENT.

00:09.070 --> 00:10.367
- THAT IS MARY LIGHTLY.

00:10.410 --> 00:12.275
HE'S VERY FAMILIAR
WITH THE PATTERNS OF OUR KILLER.

00:12.310 --> 00:13.675
- QUESTION REGARDING
THE WHOLE MARY THING.

00:13.710 --> 00:14.938
- MY FATHER'S NAME WAS MARY,

00:14.980 --> 00:16.572
HIS FATHER BEFORE HIM
WAS NAMED MARY,

00:16.610 --> 00:18.100
AND HIS FATHER
BEFORE HIM WAS NAMED CRAIG.

00:18.150 --> 00:19.811
- I FORBID YOU TO BE
A PART OF THIS, SHAWN.

00:19.850 --> 00:21.147
THIS GUY KNOWS ABOUT YOU.

00:21.180 --> 00:22.784
HE KNOWS ABOUT
EVERYBODY YOU CARE ABOUT.

00:22.820 --> 00:24.310
- HE'S GOT MY MOM.

00:24.350 --> 00:25.510
- THIS SWITCH HAS
SUCH A LIGHT TOUCH,

00:25.550 --> 00:26.517
AND THEN BOOM!

00:26.560 --> 00:27.709
- YOU'RE GONNA ROT IN A CELL

00:27.760 --> 00:29.057
WITH FOUR PADDED WALLS--
THE END.

00:29.090 --> 00:31.024
- NO, I'M GONNA WRITE A BOOK.
OUR STORY.

00:31.060 --> 00:32.027
- GUESS I HAVE
TO FIND A NEW HOBBY.

00:32.060 --> 00:33.698
- TOURS, RACQUETBALL.

00:33.730 --> 00:34.822
- THAT COULD WORK.

00:37.370 --> 00:38.564
- ALL RIGHT, SHAWN,
LAST CHANCE.

00:38.600 --> 00:40.261
YOU REALLY WANT TO DO THIS
ON A FRIDAY NIGHT?

00:40.300 --> 00:42.336
