WITHOUT GUS?

00:42.370 --> 00:44.964
- YEAH, APPARENTLY GUS
HAS A STRANGE AVERSION

00:45.010 --> 00:46.102
TO RENE AUBERJONOIS.

00:46.140 --> 00:47.801
