00:47.840 --> 00:50.001
- YOU REALLY WANT
TO SEE THIS FLICK?

00:50.050 --> 00:51.677
- DAD, DON'T SAY "FLICK."

00:51.710 --> 00:53.712
AND I'M BARELY
TICKLING ADOLESCENCE.

00:53.750 --> 00:55.570
WHY DO YOU WANT ME
TO GROW UP SO FAST?

00:55.620 --> 00:57.485
- ALL RIGHT, LISTEN, SHAWN,
I KNOW THE RUNNING TIME.

00:57.520 --> 01:00.114
I'M GONNA BE BACK HERE
IN EXACTLY 116 MINUTES.

01:00.160 --> 01:01.513
- AWESOME.

