02:47.760 --> 02:49.421
- THAT IS AN EXACT QUOTE, SHAWN.

02:49.470 --> 02:51.062
- DO YOU REMEMBER
WHAT I WAS DESCRIBED AS?

02:51.100 --> 02:53.193
- LAUGHING ON THE OUTSIDE,
CRYING ON THE INSIDE,

02:53.240 --> 02:55.629
THE FASTIDIOUS WRINKLE
ON THE BROW OF PSYCH.

02:55.670 --> 02:56.807
- TRUE, BUT SHE ALSO SAID

02:56.840 --> 02:59.308
YOU HAD SKIN OF PURE
COCOA VELVETINESS.

02:59.340 --> 03:01.274
- SHE ALSO SHE WOULD LIKE
TO USE THAT SKIN

03:01.310 --> 03:02.504
TO MAKE CHILDREN'S DOLLS.

03:02.550 --> 03:03.972
- I'D BUY THAT DOLL.

03:04.010 --> 03:04.977
THE POINT IS, SHAWN,
YOU KNOW YANG

03:05.010 --> 03:06.318
